		<title>Francophone Africa’s EV boom is held back by policy, not economics</title>
		<link>https://techcabal.com/2026/05/26/francophone-weekly-by-techcabal-024/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Lina Kacyem]]></dc:creator>
